      "利用大数据分析人流、消费习惯，科学评估点位价值，确保您的咖啡站从第一天起就占据盈利高地。",
    icon: '<svg class="w-8 h-8 brand-color" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>',
  },
  {
    title: "全链条供应链",
    description:
      "从全球精品咖啡豆直采，到仓储、物流、补货，我们提供一站式标准化供应链服务，保证品质与效率。",
    icon: '<svg class="w-8 h-8 brand-color" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z"></path></svg>',
  },
  {
    title: "专业在地运维",
    description:
      "我们遍布全国的在地化服务网络，提供快速响应的设备维护与清洁服务，确保7x24小时稳定运营。",
    icon: '<svg class="w-8 h-8 brand-color" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>',
  },
  {
    title: "数据驱动营销",
    description:
      "通过SaaS后台的用户画像与消费数据分析，我们为您策划精准的营销活动，持续提升复购率与品牌忠诚度。",
    icon: '<svg class="w-8 h-8 brand-color" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z"></path></svg>',
  },
];
---

<style>
  .feature-card {
    /* ... */
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    /* ... */
  }
</style>
<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="section-title">全方位运营服务</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle mt-4">
        我们如何让xbot的价值最大化？obubu的服务为硬件注入灵魂。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {
        services.map((service) => (
          <div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div
              class="mb-4 bg-brand-bg-light rounded-full p-3 inline-block"
              set:html={service.icon}
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">
              {service.title}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">{service.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
